graph TD
    Start[Start Pipeline] --> Validate[Validate Input]
    Validate -->|valid| Parse[Parse Data]
    Validate -->|invalid| Error[Error Handler]
    Parse --> Transform[Transform]
    Transform --> Enrich[Enrich Data]
    Enrich --> Save[Save to DB]
    Save --> Notify[Send Notification]
    Error --> Retry[Retry Logic]
    Retry -->|success| Parse
    Retry -->|failed| Alert[Alert Team]
    Notify --> End[Complete]
    Alert --> End
